{"tid":1925473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"客觀來看，七月應該係支爆可能性最大的月份。","createTime":"2020-03-14T11:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T13:34:35.000Z","uid":38861,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"80174f127230c313ecff6bba816a7d23f78350f9","tid":1925473,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T11:47:36.000Z","msg":"太空競賽一直都係各國展示國力的競爭舞台，而最接近的一場決鬥將會在2020年7月舉辦，火星探測。<br />\n<br />\n本來今次將會有四名選手「不約而同」地在7月發射攜同登陸探測器的火箭飛往火星（Ref1-5)，在火星地面上行走的登陸器（探測車）分別為<span style=\"color: red;\">NASA美國太空總署的Perseverance</span>、<span style=\"color: blue;\">俄羅斯和歐洲太空總署的Rosalind Franklin</span>、<span style=\"color: purple;\">阿拉伯聯合公國的Hope</span>以及<span style=\"color: green;\">中國的火星一號</span>。<br />\n<br />\n日前（2020年3月12日），俄羅斯和歐洲太空總署發表記招，將計劃推遲2年後舉行（Ref6)，所以今次太空競賽只剩下另外3名選手。<br />\n<br />\n雖然武肺病毒肆虐，但為了向黨成立100週年送上慶祝大禮，愛好面子的中國並無理由會打退堂鼓，連「武漢肺炎病毒可能由美軍帶來」這如此荒唐事情也能夠公開說出口的中國，又豈會做出有損國威的縮沙行為呢？<br />\n<br />\n先例早在2011年與俄羅斯合作的「螢火一號」失敗告終（Ref7，搵唔到香港報章全面報導，所以唯有引用文匯報，Sorry)，在來年的7月相信大家將有為數頗大的機會親身見證一場位於空中（甚至是國內境地）的真正支爆！<br />\n<br />\nReference:<br />\n1.https://<a href=\"http://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-00739-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fd41586-020-00739-5&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=09e67991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-00739-5</a><br />\n2.https://<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mars_2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FMars_2020&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=1965bd8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mars_2020</a><br />\n3.https://<a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2020/3/5/21163709/nasa-mars-rover-new-name-perseverance-contest-student-submissions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2020%2F3%2F5%2F21163709%2Fnasa-mars-rover-new-name-perseverance-contest-student-submissions&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=72ddeb68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.theverge.com/2020/3/5/21163709/nasa-mars-rover-new-name-perseverance-contest-student-submissions</a><br />\n4.https://<a href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%AB%E6%98%9F2020%E6%8E%A2%E6%B8%AC%E8%BB%8A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25AB%25E6%2598%259F2020%25E6%258E%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E8%25BB%258A%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258B%2599&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=2cb4795c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%AB%E6%98%9F2020%E6%8E%A2%E6%B8%AC%E8%BB%8A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99</a><br />\n5.https://<a href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%AB%E6%98%9F%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B7_(%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25AB%25E6%2598%259F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258F%25B7_%28%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=f30e2e02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%AB%E6%98%9F%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B7_(%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD</a>)<br />\n6.https://<a href=\"http://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-00746-6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fd41586-020-00746-6&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=7901af60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-00746-6</a><br />\n7.https://<a href=\"http://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-00746-6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fd41586-020-00746-6&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=7901af60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-00746-6</a>"},{"pid":"7de7c14832ce33d6e031e753cd6f977c77c4133c","tid":1925473,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T11:54:16.000Z","msg":"郭文貴：中共過埋2020年仲未收皮我就跳樓死！<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2661924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2661924&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=e20b2480\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2661924&h=4b21dc27\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2661924</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2019-01-04 16:32:40</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/06/4kDjBt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F12%2F06%2F4kDjBt.png&h=2d3a0463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n一直預告西方世界將與中國全面對抗的郭文貴還強調：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2020年是結束共產黨在中國的最後一年，否則文貴就從那18樓跳下去，大家要記住我的承諾。</strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴又爆料：中共將於今年6/4滅亡<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071249&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=ce7b3877\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071249&h=2b44cc57\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">2020-02-18 01:35:08</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/18/phpkwmUEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F18%2FphpkwmUEi.jpg&h=81372548&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n流亡美國的中國富商郭文貴不定時暴露中國高層黑幕，2月15日在直播中又爆料，共產黨推行的中國夢已經完全不可能實現，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今年6月4日「沒有共產黨的新中國一定會成立」，屆時會由世界上許多國家共同宣布。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4338c1afef9421ef5a8a0adf0c36da7e735d73e8","tid":1925473,"uid":38861,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我驚佢真係要跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880dadd0ae6502206fdbdc0e489532fc049f8ae5","tid":1925473,"uid":90304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4338c1afef9421ef5a8a0adf0c36da7e735d73e8","tid":1925473,"uid":38861,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我驚佢真係要跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:20:56.000Z","msg":"佢仲衰過老衲，到時味講句 講下笑咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61938857ebf70b5d8005a474494f58a5e5e85d90","tid":1925473,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"880dadd0ae6502206fdbdc0e489532fc049f8ae5","tid":1925473,"uid":90304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4338c1afef9421ef5a8a0adf0c36da7e735d73e8","tid":1925473,"uid":38861,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我驚佢真係要跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:20:56.000Z","msg":"佢仲衰過老衲，到時味講句 講下笑咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:23:41.000Z","msg":"或者18樓跳落去17樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e46b1c0888f33c911995a1576a0344a33f96fac","tid":1925473,"uid":202256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:28:21.000Z","msg":"樓豬標題黨<br />\n搞到我差啲開心到飛起"},{"pid":"d8796b11caa30ea0e14c1ac93edd1bceb65faf70","tid":1925473,"uid":38861,"like"